<cleanup>
Stop app:
```
stop_app_sim({
  simulatorUuid: "B6E73094-CED6-458D-B9F5-9D65034F10E0",
  bundleId: "com.vkosmirak.AgenticClock"
})
```

Clean build:
```
clean({
  projectPath: "AgenticClock/AgenticClock.xcodeproj",
  scheme: "AgenticClock",
  platform: "iOS Simulator"
})
```
